        <item>
            <title>Bing 搜尋將 AI 結果擺在正中間，全新 Generative Search 將以往搜尋結果擺一邊</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/microsoft-bing-new-layout-for-ai-search/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-bing-new-layout-for-ai-search</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/microsoft-bing-new-layout-for-ai-search/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 10:30:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI Overviews]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Bing Generative Search]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Microsoft Bing]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1252794</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft 正計劃為旗下搜尋引擎 Bing 推出 Generative Search 功能，這將會與 Google Search 早前推出的 AI Overviews 功能十分相似。目前 Microsoft 邀請了部分用户為這個新功能進行測試，相信很快就會開放使用。</p><figure id="attachment_1252798" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1252798" style="width: 599px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1252798 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/how_long_can_elephan-599x580.jpeg" alt="" width="599" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/how_long_can_elephan-599x580.jpeg 599w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/how_long_can_elephan-scaled.jpeg 929w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 599px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1252798" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲Bing 正在測試的新介面</span></figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1252804" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1252804" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" class="wp-image-1252804 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-2-scaled-e1721899013366-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-2-scaled-e1721899013366-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13-2-scaled-e1721899013366-1280x713.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1252804" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲目前 Bing 的搜尋介面</span></figcaption></figure><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://blogs.bing.com/search/July-2024/generativesearch">Bing Blogs</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft Bing 將與大語言模型和小語言模型結合，理解搜尋內容並查閲上百萬個資料來源，動態匹配內容，並在新的介面中生成出搜尋結果。Bing 的新介面將原本搜尋結果會顯示的所有網站連結移到右方，而由人工智能整合內容後生成的答覆則會在畫面的正中央，往下滾動會顯示搜尋內容的額外資訊，例如相關的影片、歷史資訊和圖表等，Bing 亦會在每個資訊下方列出來源。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Microsoft 推出這款 Generative Search 功能的時候有考慮到會影響其他網站的搜尋流量，早期數據中表明 Generative Search 功能將會保留網站的點擊數並維持一個健康的網絡生態系統。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/24/24205404/bing-ai-search-redesign?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2FhhKWjeQ81UflTjcTmZHXXu0-1ZAznbdPLTkjmFADOj6bRMgVVdZQQvw_aem_uDpisJWQHI3uUvILCl8qqQ">The Verge</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://blogs.bing.com/search/July-2024/generativesearch">Bing Blogs</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/14/head-of-googlesearch-admits-aioverviews-error/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Google 承認 AI Overviews 功能會出錯   「公司願意冒犯錯的風險繼續前進」</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/microsoft-bing-new-layout-for-ai-search/ai/">Bing 搜尋將 AI 結果擺在正中間，全新 Generative Search 將以往搜尋結果擺一邊</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/25/microsoft-bing-new-layout-for-ai-search/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
